5. CONFIDENTIALITY
================================================================================

The Internal Components constitute confidential information of Trustwise. You
shall protect Internal Components using reasonable care. CLI Tool commands,
flags, output formats, documentation, and usage patterns are NOT confidential
and may be discussed freely.

Confidentiality obligations survive termination for three (3) years or for so
long as the Internal Components remain trade secrets, whichever is longer.

